113
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:04,079
Bye. Take care, take care!

114
00:08:04,079 --> 00:08:08,539
President Lu, do you want to be Miss Su's consultant for romance novels?

115
00:08:08,539 --> 00:08:11,060
