169
00:11:40,140 --> 00:11:43,180
[Domineering CEO's Warm-Hearted New Wife, Chapter One: He gently lay her on the bed. He gazed at her softly, while she stared back at him with love.]

170
00:11:43,180 --> 00:11:45,779
